{"tid":2332680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來係醫院檢疫期間逃走 最高刑罰都係$5000及監禁兩個月","createTime":"2020-12-19T19:52:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T02:38:34.000Z","uid":54373,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7ff8a815b1c458f1a1cdf2c105d218ea8a5a3eef","tid":2332680,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T19:52:04.000Z","msg":"警方表示根據法例，如任何在醫院等場所內被檢疫或隔離的人逃走，即屬犯罪，可判處罰款5000元及監禁2個月。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n確診左都有$5000，罰$5000咪當無袋<br />\n<br />\n仲有一定係初犯，再認罪<br />\n分分鐘社會服務令都唔使<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">李運強，快d揀間警署自首啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"03ebb8b56d97fef9edb9ccaa95961f32d7383a41","tid":2332680,"uid":208940,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T20:07:45.000Z","msg":"走犯都係判咁輕？？？唔怪之得四維走<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無戴口罩都5千蚊啦！！！！"},{"pid":"8b9e19f6c9e4014d0a1d4941d7a0dd734542339d","tid":2332680,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T01:08:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca9e93b2bd4f0b96df59a7955749072371f99a02","tid":2332680,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T01:10:30.000Z","msg":"如果係黃絲，doj會加控你危害國家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9394bd6fca92c52e857b4ab2e7208c147d4930af","tid":2332680,"uid":62850,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T01:12:03.000Z","msg":"香港真係逃犯天堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81677d12138050b9b85a28f0761aee00d004422e","tid":2332680,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T01:12:28.000Z","msg":"應該係監禁六個月<br />\n29.出入限制<br />\n(1)任何人不得離開該人被檢疫或隔離所在的地方。<br />\n(2)除衞生主任外，任何人不得在未獲根據第31條給予的書面准許下 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)進入另一人被檢疫或隔離所在的地方；或<br />\n(b)進入或離開受隔離的地方。<br />\n(3)任何人違反第(1)或(2)款，即屬犯罪，一經定罪，可處第2級罰款及監禁6個月。"},{"pid":"61632f2135d4aa073e240b841c0ade2fbb6c3788","tid":2332680,"uid":1654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T01:17:40.000Z","msg":"熱愛射檜、高尚呈醋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c4a2a94087fd073e861aae3f85c5f77a0e70d2","tid":2332680,"uid":156913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T01:39:00.000Z","msg":"on9 政府, 要告就告國安法<br />\n<blockquote>恐怖活動罪<br />\n第二十四條 為脅迫中央人民政府、香港特別行政區政府或者國際組織或者威嚇公眾以圖實現政治主張，組織、策劃、實施、參與實施或者威脅實施以下造成或者意圖造成嚴重社會危害的恐怖活動之一的，即屬犯罪：<br />\n  （一）針對人的嚴重暴力；<br />\n  （二）爆炸、縱火或者<span class=\"red\">投放毒害性、放射性、傳染病病原體等物質</span>；<br />\n  （三）破壞運輸工具、運輸設施、電力設備、燃氣設備或者其他易燃易爆設備；<br />\n  （四）嚴重干擾、破壞水、電、燃氣、運輸、通訊、網絡等公共服務和管理的電子控制系統；<br />\n<span class=\"red\">  （五）以其他危險方法嚴重危害公眾健康或者安全。 </span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5b5a6ff07193458f8656df3ce9b010ea6c5885b6","tid":2332680,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T01:40:54.000Z","msg":"說好的國安法呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc53c3921d0e417c7311c246535d44afcbc